<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">

<head>
  <meta charset="UTF-8">
  <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
  <meta http-equiv="X-UA-Compatible" content="ie=edge">
  <title>Manthan - 2020 | MANAN</title>
  <link href="https://maxcdn.bootstrapcdn.com/font-awesome/4.7.0/css/font-awesome.min.css" rel="stylesheet"
    integrity="sha384-wvfXpqpZZVQGK6TAh5PVlGOfQNHSoD2xbE+QkPxCAFlNEevoEH3Sl0sibVcOQVnN" crossorigin="anonymous">
  <link rel="stylesheet" href="https://cdnjs.cloudflare.com/ajax/libs/animate.css/3.5.2/animate.css" />
  <link rel="stylesheet" href="index.css">
</head>

<body>
  <% if(message.length> 0) { %>
    <div class="alert">
      <span class="closebtn" onclick="this.parentElement.style.display='none';">&times;</span>
      <strong>OOps!</strong>
      <%= message %>
    </div>
    <% } %>
      <div class="container">
        <h1 class="brand block">
          <span><img src="./images/MANAN-logo-1.jpg" id="logo" alt="logo"></span>
          <span> Manthan</span>
          <span style="color: rgb(216, 204, 204);"><b>2020</b></span>
        </h1>

        <div class="instruction-text animated bounceInLeft">
          <h2>Instructions</h2>
          <ul>
            <li>
              <b>Round 1 for 1st Year:</b><br>
              After a few days of registering, you will receive a link by mail for the aptitude test which will be held
              on
              January 18, 2020. This round is mandatory for everyone in first year to participate in.
            </li>
            <li>
              <br>
              <b>Round 2 for 2nd Year:</b><br>
              After a few days of registering, you will receive a link by mail for the Competitive Coding Round which
              will be held on January 18, 2020. This round is mandatory for everyone in second year to participate in.
              <br>
              After that, we will have Project and CP showcasing rounds. After the test, you will receive instructions
              to book your showcasing interviews. In Project showcasing you will be expected to show a working model of
              your work and answer some questions related to it. In CP showcasing you will be expected to know the
              basics of CP and answer a few CP questions and walk us with your approach. Both of these rounds are not
              mandatory. These are just to help us assess you better in terms of your technical skills.
              <br>
              We will then amalgamate the scores of all these together to have a final standing. We will filter out the
              deserving candidates and call them to a personal interview.
            </li>
            <li>
              <br>
              <b>For 3rd Year:</b><br>
              We will be asking you guys to submit your CV and social profile links like GitHub, CodeForces and will
              call the right candidates to the personal interview.
              <br>
            </li>
            <li>
              <br>
              <b>Personal Interview:</b><br>
              If you receive a mail/message for the PI, then we will check that whether you are a perfect fit for us or
              not. If yes, we will invite you to be a Mananite.
              <br>
            </li>
          </ul>

        </div>
        <div class="audition-process">
          <img src="./images/audition_process_web.png" alt="" width="50%" height="30%"
            style="display: block; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto;">
          <div style="margin-bottom:50px;">
            <button class="button2 register-now-btn">
              <a class="go-to-registration-form" href="#registration-form"> Register Now </a>
            </button>
          </div>
        </div>

        <div class="wrapper animated bounceInLeft">
          <div class="company-info">
            <ul>
              <li><i class="fa fa-road"></i> Contact Us.</li>
              <li><i class="fa fa-phone"></i> 7015266612 (Sahil)</li>
              <li><i class="fa fa-envelope"></i> manantechnosurge@gmail.com</li>
            </ul>
          </div>
          <div class="contact">
            <h3>Register</h3>
            <form action="/addUser" method="POST" id="registration-form">
              <p>
                <input id="name" name="fullname" type="text" class="validate" required="" aria-required="true">
                <label for="name">Full Name*</label>
              </p>
              <p>
                <input id="roll_no" name="rollno" type="text" class="validate" aria-required="true">
                <label for="roll_no">Roll No eg. 18001003076</label>
              </p>
              <p>
                <input class="validate" id="email" name="email" type="email" required="" aria-required="true">
                <label for="email" data-error="wrong" data-success="right" class="center-align">Email*</label>
              </p>
              <p>
                <input id="contact_no" name="phone" type="text" class="validate" required="" aria-required="true"
                  value="+91">
                <label for="contact_no">Contact No*</label>
              </p>
              <p>
                <select name="branch" id="branch" required="">
                  <option value="" disabled selected>Choose your option</option>
                  <option value="CE">Computers</option>
                  <option value="IT">Information Technology</option>
                  <option value="ECS">ECS</option>
                  <option value="EL">Electrical</option>
                  <option value="ECE">ECE</option>
                  <option value="EIC">EIC</option>
                  <option value="Civil">Civil</option>
                  <option value="ME">Mechanical</option>
                </select>
                <label>Branch*</label>
              </p>
              <p>
                <select name="year" id="year" required="">
                  <option value="" disabled selected>Choose your option</option>
                  <option value="1">1st</option>
                  <option value="2">2nd</option>
                  <option value="3">3rd</option>
                </select>
                <label>Year*</label>
              </p>
              <p>
                <input type="text" name="codingprofilelinks">
                <label>Coding Profile Links</label>
              </p>
              <p>
                <input type="text" name="opensourcelinks">
                <label>OpenSource Links</label>
              </p>
              <p>
                <input type="text" name="otherprofiles">
                <label>Other Profiles</label>
              </p>
              <p>
                <input type="text" name="CV">
                <label>CV/Resume (GDrive Link) compulsory for 3rd year</label>
              </p>
              <p class="full">
                <button>Submit</button>
              </p>
            </form>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
</body>

</html>